# Tell UI rules

Follow `docs/01_DESIGN_SYSTEM.md`. Dogfood: Tell must not trigger its own tells.

- Fonts: Instrument Serif + Source Sans 3 + IBM Plex Mono — **never Inter-only**
- No violet gradient hero, no shadow on every card
- Use semantic Tailwind tokens: `bg-surface`, `text-secondary`, `text-accent`
- Raw hex belongs in `globals.css` tokens only, not TSX classNames
- Full state matrix on interactive components: hover, focus-visible, active, disabled, loading/error where applicable
- Preserve the signature `BeforeAfterSeam`; keyboard and reduced-motion behavior are part of the feature
- Copy from USER_STORY.md copy bank — critic voice, no emoji chrome
- Hero = Tell Report + reveal seam, not KPI dashboard
- Current UI is mostly `apps/web/src/app/page.tsx`; extract components only when it reduces real complexity

Use `@ui-builder` (Composer) for components; `@ux-copywriter` (GPT 5.5) for copy polish.
